{"tid":31940,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇「只有乞食既人，冇乞食科」呢句野？","createTime":"2016-12-10T02:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-04T01:51:06.000Z","uid":24006,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d1fbe5da9f7967610799528e851b12baa914fac","tid":31940,"uid":24006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:51:41.000Z","msg":"成日見到d人用黎為乞食科既存在辯護<br />\n話你搵唔到食係因為你自己廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我心諗，大把有料既人grad左都冇前途，咁唔知又關唔關科垃圾事呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8568c349469c252dc5f841bf8eb630aadf8248fa","tid":31940,"uid":42217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20110214/large/14la1p101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20110214%2Flarge%2F14la1p101.jpg&h=db56fb7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6b24f65c8576ec12ba64d8a7050f137c9735ded","tid":31940,"uid":33631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:06:24.000Z","msg":"垃圾先會入乞食科(e.g.三大最低分嘅cu engine)<br />\n垃圾本身就要乞食"},{"pid":"4c7a7ec28c4440eccd28747ad54fa75c8f0bf57c","tid":31940,"uid":27066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:12:23.000Z","msg":"就算入咗所謂嘅乞食科，都唔一定註定你一世乞食架喎<br />\n講真你讀大學嗰時唔好掛住玩啊上莊啊拍拖乜乜物物嗰啲，有時間攞嚟學吓嘢，例如外語，做到自己喺將來嗰行可以人無我有，甚至可能成功轉到行都未定<br />\n<br />\n沒有廢人，只有懶嘅廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d51e998ea75d6deab90f3c22559b0c14b43311d","tid":31940,"uid":52342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:46:34.000Z","msg":"講得出只有廢人無廢科呢句既人<br />\n肯肯定佢地無入過世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc0fddc513021f246455a32bd379c61a520e0e4","tid":31940,"uid":24006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:48:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cdd8b582de840a1616fc9d8ea7fdb385c04c78d8","tid":31940,"uid":25573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:52:16.000Z","msg":"通常係讀乞食科既人先咁講<br />\n自己呃自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ce3a76e845943fdddb19b6db99dffc2a735c24","tid":31940,"uid":22808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講得出只有廢人無廢科呢句既人<br />\n肯肯定佢地無入過世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實黎，搵食專科幾可有廢人？<br />\n廢科入面嘅勁人，假假地都做個研究生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a1ac0f2923d6160ebdbfe1c1bfe523de4a0648","tid":31940,"uid":24006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T23:51:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講得出只有廢人無廢科呢句既人<br />\n肯肯定佢地無入過世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實黎，搵食專科幾可有廢人？<br />\n廢科入面嘅勁人，假假地都做個研究生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n響香港做研究搵到食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd35d7838750c4f1364c9c8240c949e1c2ca468a","tid":31940,"uid":59746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T23:53:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講得出只有廢人無廢科呢句既人<br />\n肯肯定佢地無入過世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實黎，搵食專科幾可有廢人？<br />\n廢科入面嘅勁人，假假地都做個研究生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n響香港做研究搵到食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做到既穩袋6,7粒未計其他野<br />\n係要求好高姐"},{"pid":"b54a2f8e8eb40deee8bdd6d59f2496a4c7dcdac6","tid":31940,"uid":24006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:53:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"453c9268b30c3d5532a39ed98c6a0408dfbcb058","tid":31940,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:15:36.000Z","msg":"只有乞食嘅科,無乞食嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每科fresh grad出嚟都唔同價,有d乞食科出嚟最低工資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869f3f1a8d7a81f339b49e377dfe66600e8bf463","tid":31940,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T13:19:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算入咗所謂嘅乞食科，都唔一定註定你一世乞食架喎<br />\n講真你讀大學嗰時唔好掛住玩啊上莊啊拍拖乜乜物物嗰啲，有時間攞嚟學吓嘢，例如外語，做到自己喺將來嗰行可以人無我有，甚至可能成功轉到行都未定<br />\n<br />\n沒有廢人，只有懶嘅廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我大學四年無拍拖，專心讀書無走堂，交齊功課，平時去圖書館睇書溫書，睇日劇學日語<br />\n畢業四年都係搵唔到長工， 靠合約工"},{"pid":"12e29716e378c9095119276374e9087527bee605","tid":31940,"uid":24623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T13:22:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就算入咗所謂嘅乞食科，都唔一定註定你一世乞食架喎<br />\n講真你讀大學嗰時唔好掛住玩啊上莊啊拍拖乜乜物物嗰啲，有時間攞嚟學吓嘢，例如外語，做到自己喺將來嗰行可以人無我有，甚至可能成功轉到行都未定<br />\n<br />\n沒有廢人，只有懶嘅廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我大學四年無拍拖，專心讀書無走堂，交齊功課，平時去圖書館睇書溫書，睇日劇學日語<br />\n畢業四年都係搵唔到長工， 靠合約工</blockquote><br />\n我成日覺得讀大學 擴闊眼界/社交圈子&gt;死讀書"},{"pid":"0ea5772460cfbe539c824e150c5b43a3fa80eb8a","tid":31940,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T13:26:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a79ae6134f9a6619f2c660cf3c0b365e67bfaf01","tid":31940,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T13:30:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實黎，搵食專科幾可有廢人？<br />\n廢科入面嘅勁人，假假地都做個研究生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n響香港做研究搵到食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做到既穩袋6,7粒未計其他野<br />\n係要求好高姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啲料的人要去國讀phd 其實一啲都唔難<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解香港fg 唔識放眼國際"},{"pid":"010b5a0da29cfdfee82a3d15980fafb518c128e8","tid":31940,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n響香港做研究搵到食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做到既穩袋6,7粒未計其他野<br />\n係要求好高姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啲料的人要去國讀phd 其實一啲都唔難<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解香港fg 唔識放眼國際</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你真係好傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8537826f727e1b23ff1cae109b47539426c0d040","tid":31940,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T17:09:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做到既穩袋6,7粒未計其他野<br />\n係要求好高姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啲料的人要去國讀phd 其實一啲都唔難<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解香港fg 唔識放眼國際</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你真係好傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點on9你又唔講"},{"pid":"84d83b43aaa2f5bc0ab38d309bef3a27ec1aa839","tid":31940,"uid":3626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T17:50:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只有乞食嘅科,無乞食嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每科fresh grad出嚟都唔同價,有d乞食科出嚟最低工資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a18580206fd78a72745199e8414a30a9d042f8","tid":31940,"uid":56899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T19:38:37.000Z","msg":"同行行出狀元一樣"},{"pid":"c264c7c34af1de9